<br>
If you can arrange it, don't do transfers in the bazaar.  On 3 separate occasions thus far, started after one of the last patches, I would put something in the transfer window to someone.  The other person would say that it didn't show up on their transfer window.  At this point, the item can be considered gone.  If you hit trade, the item disappears, if you hit cancel the item disappears, if you hit the x in top corner, the item disappears.  It only seems to happen in the bazaar.  GM's have replaced the items on all three occasions its happened to me(or my wifes trader).  Thats all I can say about it, besides the fact that having 2 blessed fishing rods going poof was not a very happy occasion.  Thanks again to Lavela for your help in this matter.<br>
